{"tid":153935,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"台每月逾百部LG V10 過熱死機","createTime":"2017-03-13T02:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T03:03:59.000Z","uid":60817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd15d99f857eedc7ca197b213048d0b1dee8c486","tid":153935,"uid":60817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T02:16:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">台每月逾百部LG V10 過熱死機</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170313/large/a1506a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170313%2Flarge%2Fa1506a.gif&h=81b3a9a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓系手機又現問題！去年南韓三星Note7手機發生多宗自爆事件，震驚全球，未料另一款南韓LG V10手機，也在台灣傳出手機主機板過熱導致無法開機，目前已有超過100名消費者投訴。LG公司坦承手機有瑕疵，目前仍在調查過熱原因。<br />\n從事電子業的張先生向台灣《蘋果日報》投訴，去年初花2萬多元新台幣（5,000多港元）購買V10（圖），後來發現手機經常過熱及死機，至去年10月無法開機，送往修理後得知主機板過熱故障。張先生之後發現台灣至少有逾百名LG V10的用戶發生類似情形，其後張獲多名機主委託向台北市消保官投訴，但LG堅持不提供免費更換服務，眾機主目前正商討是否循法律途徑索償。<br />\n台灣LG回應，目前每月約100宗V10維修個案，並不全是硬體瑕疵或過熱故障造成，有些是軟體問題或消費者使用不當造成，暫無法提供免費更換，但願意以優惠價維修手機。<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170313/19956439\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170313%2F19956439&d=vI%2FQCok0BRDS6jHm%2BKkcarZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=e684042d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170313%2F19956439&h=224af961\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170313/19956439</a><br />\n垃圾LG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9b9ccd7aa4c8ad73d3a73c10f528b7c7ec6f9f","tid":153935,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:18:14.000Z","msg":"想拎 LG  boot loop 畫面做wallpaper<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dac1a3de053499a0d2dfdfc8d